data.description: Lake Life in Fayetteville! Welcome Home and set your eyes on this beautiful 2-story brick front home! This amazingly well-maintained home is nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac of the sought after swim/tennis Heritage Lake community. This beautiful home features 5 bedrooms, 3 1/2 bathroom, an expansive deck over looking the lake and fully equipped and finished basement. Upon entry of this home you will find high ceilings in the foyer which expands to the formal living room featuring cathedral ceilings and chaired railings throughout. From the great room, enjoy the beautiful lake view amongst the large arched windows ensuring the ultimate sunlight in the family room and kitchen while delighting in quality time with your family. Gorgeous chef's kitchen with stainless appliances and lots of storage overlooks the beautiful lake. On the second level take pleasure in the oversized primary suite displaying high tray ceilings and hardwood flooring. Entering the master bathroom with updated frameless shower, spa like tub and a large walk-in closet. This level also features 3 additional room, 2 of which are Jack and Jill bedrooms and an additional bedroom with plenty of space within. This home also includes a fully finished basement including but not limited to a completed kitchen, bathroom, living room, and two additional bedrooms. The basement also has two entry doors which provides private access from the beautiful backyard. This home is has convenient access to major interstates, an international airport, a top U.S. golf course, shopping, dining, and a major studio and so much more. Your new home awaits!
